A modern and fully responsive contact form built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript with smooth animations and a clean, professional UI.

This project includes real backend integration using Formspree, allowing users to send messages directly to email. It is fully compatible with GitHub Pages and suitable for portfolio and freelance websites.

